<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login - AquaSis</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 flex h-screen">

    <div class="hidden md:flex md:w-1/2 bg-sky-900 flex-col justify-center items-center p-12 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-96 h-96 bg-sky-800 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-96 h-96 bg-sky-700 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
        
        <div class="z-10 text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial text-5xl text-sky-300"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AquaSis</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-sky-200 font-light max-w-md mx-auto">Gestão laboratorial inteligente para análises químicas e físicas.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex items-center justify-center p-8 bg-white">
        <div class="w-full max-w-md">
            
            <div class="md:hidden text-center mb-8">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial text-4xl text-sky-600 mb-2"></i>
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">AquaSis</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">Acesso Restrito</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">Insira suas credenciais para acessar a plataforma.</p>
            </div>

            {{#if erroLogin}}
            <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 text-red-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">{{erroLogin}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <form action="/login" method="POST">
                <div class="mb-5">
                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">E-mail Corporativo</label>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-slate-400"></i>
                        </div>
                        <input type="email" name="email" class="w-full pl-10 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2.5 outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500 transition-shadow" placeholder="quimico@laboratorio.com" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Senha</label>
                        <a href="#" class="text-xs font-medium text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-800 transition-colors">Esqueceu a senha?</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-lock text-slate-400"></i>
                        </div>
                        <input type="password" name="senha" class="w-full pl-10 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2.5 outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500 transition-shadow" placeholder="••••••••" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-sky-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-sky-700 shadow-md shadow-sky-200 transition-all active:scale-[0.98]">
                    Entrar no Sistema <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-to-bracket ml-2"></i>
                </button>
            </form>

            <div class="mt-8 text-center text-xs text-slate-400">
                <p>&copy; 2026 AquaSis. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>